{
  "stem": "27351.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother was going crazy about what happened to [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we found him safe at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They never took any part in any fight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Czestochowa did not fight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came back to here, where it happened in Czestochowa on Sunday, which means on the third day of the war we were still on the road.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On this-- no, it was Monday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in on Sunday, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on Monday, they rounded up hundreds and hundreds of people, Jews and Poles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, at that time-- at that moment, they didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They marched them through the city, beating them, and hitting them, and ridiculing them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they machine gunned a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only heard it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't see any of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this day was called the Bloody Monday in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this was the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Jews right from the beginning started to pray.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans, particularly Jews in traditional grab Jews with beards, right away they started to cut the beards, to ask these Jews to jump in the streets like dogs, like rabbits, like groups of soldiers just looking at it, and laughing their heads off, and making pictures.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This started right away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But, of course, nobody, nobody, could ever imagine what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, our imagination did not go that far.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So Jews like Jews-- you know, Jews were used to different times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, well, we'll survive this too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have to be careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We have to, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, I didn't stay long in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Were their restrictions that came into effect before you left?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, right away, there were restrictions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
